statements: SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults;
SELECT id, algorithm_name, error_correction_technique FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT algorithm_name, error_correction_technique, error_rate FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults WHERE error_rate > 0.05;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT id, algorithm_name, error_rate FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults ORDER BY error_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT algorithm_name, error_correction_technique, error_rate FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults WHERE error_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY error_rate DESC
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults WHERE algorithm_name = 'Shor' AND error_rate < 0.1
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults
SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(*) FROM QuantumErrorCorrectionResults GROUP BY algorithm_name ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_correction_results;
SELECT error_count, algorithm_name FROM quantum_error_correction_results ORDER BY error_count DESC;
SELECT correction_technique, algorithm_name FROM quantum_error_correction_results WHERE error_count > 5;
SELECT result_id, algorithm_name FROM quantum_error_correction_results WHERE correction_technique LIKE '%quantum%';
SELECT result_id, log_timestamp, log_details FROM quantum_error_correction_logs;
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_correction_results WHERE error_count > 5 ORDER BY algorithm_name ASC;
SELECT result_id, algorithm_name FROM quantum_error_correction_results WHERE error_count = 0;
SELECT algorithm_name, correction_technique FROM quantum_error_correction_results WHERE error_count > 10 ORDER BY error_count DESC;
SELECT r.algorithm_name, l.log_timestamp, l.log_details FROM quantum_error_correction_results r JOIN quantum_error_correction_logs l ON r.result_id = l.result_id;

SELECT r.algorithm_name, l.log_timestamp, l.log_details FROM quantum_error_correction_results r LEFT JOIN quantum_error_correction_logs l ON r.result_id = l.result_id WHERE r.error_count <= 5 ORDER BY l.log_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrors;
SELECT error_id, error_type FROM QuantumErrors WHERE error_id = 1;
SELECT code_type, code_description FROM QuantumCodes ORDER BY code_type DESC;
SELECT result_data FROM QuantumResults WHERE error_id = 2 AND code_id = 3;
SELECT error_description AS error FROM QuantumErrors WHERE error_id = 3;
SELECT error_id, error_type, error_description FROM QuantumErrors;
SELECT code_id, code_type, code_description FROM QuantumCodes ORDER BY code_id DESC;
SELECT result_id, error_id, code_id, result_data FROM QuantumResults WHERE error_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM QuantumCodes JOIN QuantumResults ON QuantumCodes.code_id = QuantumResults.code_id;
SELECT * FROM QuantumResults WHERE result_data LIKE '%error%' OR result_data LIKE '%code%' ORDER BY result_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_correction;
SELECT error_id, description FROM quantum_error_correction;
SELECT error_name, probability FROM error_types;
SELECT qubit_id, error_type FROM qubits ORDER BY qubit_id DESC;
SELECT log_id, error_id, qubit_id, timestamp FROM error_logs WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_correction;
SELECT error_id, description FROM quantum_error_correction ORDER BY error_id DESC;
SELECT qubit_id, error_type FROM qubits WHERE error_type = 2;

SELECT error_logs.log_id, quantum_error_correction.description, error_types.error_name FROM error_logs INNER JOIN quantum_error_correction ON error_logs.error_id = quantum_error_correction.error_id INNER JOIN error_types ON error_logs.qubit_id = error_types.type_id;
SELECT qubit_id, error_type, probability FROM qubits INNER JOIN error_types ON qubits.error_type = error_types.type_id ORDER BY probability DESC;
SELECT * FROM error_correction_results;
SELECT result_id, error_correction_code, error_probability FROM error_correction_results WHERE number_of_qubits > 5;
SELECT code_name, code_description FROM error_correction_codes ORDER BY code_name DESC;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE algorithm_name LIKE '%Grover%';
SELECT qubit_id, qubit_state FROM qubits WHERE qubit_state = '0';
SELECT * FROM error_correction_results ORDER BY error_probability DESC, number_of_qubits ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT result_id, number_of_qubits, error_correction_code FROM error_correction_results WHERE error_probability < 0.05 AND number_of_qubits >= 5;
SELECT code_name, code_description FROM error_correction_codes WHERE LENGTH(code_description) > 20 ORDER BY code_name ASC;
SELECT qubit_id, qubit_state FROM qubits WHERE qubit_state = '0' OR qubit_state = '1' ORDER BY qubit_id DESC LIMIT 3;

SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(*) FROM quantum_algorithms JOIN error_correction_results ON quantum_algorithms.algorithm_id = error_correction_results.quantum_algorithm_id GROUP BY algorithm_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
